lixir-252-riding-the-tidewave-of-ai-enhanced-phoenix&#34;&gt;View on ElixirStatus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;            &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/table&gt;&#xA;        】&lt;table width =“ 100％” border =“ 0”&gt;&#xA;            &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td宽度= 80 valign = top&gt;&#xA;                &lt;img src =“ https://elixirstatus.com/rss/avatar/brainlid?uid=gmrai” width =“ 64”高=“ 64”/&gt;&#xA;              &lt;/td&gt;&#xA;              &lt;td&gt;&#xA;                &lt;h1&gt;思考Elixir 252：乘坐Ai-Enhanced Phoenix &lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;font color =“＃aaa”&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color =“＃aaa”&gt;&#xA;                     2025年5月6日&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color =“＃aaa”&gt;&#xA;                    经过&#xA;                    &lt;i class =“ icon-git_circle”&gt; &lt;/i&gt; Brainlid&#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                  &lt;font color =“＃aaa”&gt;&#xA;                    &#xA;                  &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;                &lt;/font&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;p&gt;&#xA;第252集的&lt;a href =“ https://podcast.thinkingelixir.com”&gt;思考Elixir &lt;/a&gt;。 News includes Tidewave, a new Phoenix MCP server that helps AI-enabled editors access application runtime, Chris McCord teasing his AI-enabled Phoenix app with LiveView hosted IDE features, a new GitHub Action for submitting Elixir dependencies to enhance security, ExMeralda.chat, a community chatbot for querying Hex packages, updates on Software Mansion’s LiveDebugger v0.2.0于5月，混合测试。用于增强的Exunit测试工作流程以及有关SlopsQuatting的信息，针对AI辅助开发人员的新恶意软件技术等等！&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&lt;a href =“ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ab2kuxm2xvm”&gt; https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ab2kuxm2xvm &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;                &lt;hr&gt;&#xA;                &lt;small&gt; &lt;A href =“ https://elixirstatus.com/p/gmrai-thinking-elixir-252-riding-the-tidewave-oai-enhanced-phoenix-&#xA;           